<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
	<p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">
		Please reach us at
		<a href="mailto:info@tlvmasterclass.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"> info@tlvmasterclass.com </a>
		if you cannot find an answer to your question.
	</p>

	<!-- FAQ Items Container -->
	<div class="mt-8 space-y-4 my-0 mx-auto max-w-[1000px]">
		<!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Why is this program specifically targeted toward African leaders?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">The Leadership Voice Masterclass is designed to address the unique challenges and opportunities African leaders face in global and regional leadership. It equips them with the communication skills, strategic influence, and confidence needed to navigate leadership roles effectively across diverse industries, ensuring their voices are heard on global platforms.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">What if I am not African but have a need for this class?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">The Leadership Voice Masterclass is open to women and men from all backgrounds and nationalities. While the program is designed with a strong focus on empowering African leaders, its core principles—enhancing communication, leadership presence, and confidence—are universal. If you believe this masterclass aligns with your leadership goals, we encourage you to register and participate, either in-person or virtually.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">If I’ve paid in full but something comes up, can I switch to another session?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">Yes. We understand that schedules can change. If you notify us ahead of time, your payment can be applied to a future TLV session of your choice.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Will the group sessions be held in person in 2025?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">Yes. In 2025, the in-person group sessions will take place in multiple locations, which will be announced soon. Additional locations may be added based on demand. Full details on schedules will be provided ahead of registration. If your location isn’t included, you can still join the program virtually.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Can I pay for the program in instalments?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">Yes, you can pay in instalments; however, full payment must be received before the start of your selected session. To request an installment plan, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@tlvmasterclass.com" class="hover:underline">info@tlvmasterclass.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Why is the fee quoted in USD and not the local currency?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">The fee is quoted in USD to ensure consistency and transparency for all participants, regardless of location. This simplifies international transactions and allows us to accommodate participants from multiple countries. However, payments can be made in local currency at the prevailing exchange rate at the time of payment. For assistance, please contact <a href="mailto:info@tlvmasterclass.com" class="hover:underline">info@tlvmasterclass.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Will I have access to the recorded materials after the session?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">Yes. All participants receive access to session recordings and key learning materials to help reinforce your learning and allow for continued reflection.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>

		<!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
		<div class="faq-item">
			<button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-lg transition-colors">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white font-pf ">Can I get an assessment before enrolling in the program?</h2>
				<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white transform transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
				</svg>
			</button>
			<div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 bg-[#0c3030] rounded-b-lg">
				<p class="text-gray-400">Yes. To help you determine if TLV is the right fit for your leadership journey, we offer a pre-enrolment assessment. Please email us at <a href="mailto:info@tlvmasterclass.com" class="hover:underline">info@tlvmasterclass.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="border-[#291ebc] my-4" />
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<script>
	document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
		const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll(".faq-item");

		faqItems.forEach((item) => {
			const button = item.querySelector("button");
			const answer = item.querySelector(".faq-answer");
			const arrow = button.querySelector("svg");

			button.addEventListener("click", () => {
				// Toggle the answer visibility
				answer.classList.toggle("hidden");

				// Rotate the arrow
				arrow.classList.toggle("rotate-180");

				// Optional: Close other open items
				faqItems.forEach((otherItem) => {
					if (otherItem !== item) {
						const otherAnswer = otherItem.querySelector(".faq-answer");
						const otherArrow = otherItem.querySelector("svg");
						otherAnswer.classList.add("hidden");
						otherArrow.classList.remove("rotate-180");
					}
				});
			});
		});
	});
</script>
